sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant Plume
  participant Kithara
  participant Auth as Auth adapter MVP

  User->>Plume: Open /
  Plume->>Kithara: GET /api/auth/discovery
  Kithara->>Plume: auth_providers.json
  Plume->>User: Auth selection and forms
  User->>Plume: Submit auth form
  Plume->>Auth: Authenticate
  Auth-->>Plume: token
